            <h1 class="text-center mb-5">Rules &amp; Regulations</h1>
            <ol class="fs-5">
              <li>
                It is highly recommended that participants utilize a laptop or computer to partake in the event.
              </li>
              <li>
                The event comprises three distinct tiers, each characterized by a unique theme and a progressively increasing level of difficulty.
              </li>
              <li>
                Upon successfully conquering a given level, participants will then proceed to the subsequent tier.
              </li>
              <li>
                It is strongly recommended that contestants refrain from closing the tab or refreshing the page during the hunt, as doing so may lead to the loss of their progress.
              </li>
              <li>
                The criteria for victory is predicated on the completion of the entire quest in the shortest possible time.
              </li>
              <li>
                If any member of a team is found to be engaging in any unethical behavior, they will be disqualified from further participation in the event.
              </li>
            </ol>
